{"tid":96972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[求聯署］要求特區政府立即交代其防止自殺政策","createTime":"2017-01-27T09:56:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T14:35:19.000Z","uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8a8c953c8dafad7caf91b6dd6154d071b301d453","tid":96972,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T09:56:23.000Z","msg":"香港的自殺率高企，可是特區政府一直掉以輕心。失業失戀有精神病紀錄大致上為其「死因」，看報紙警方多以「死因無可疑」結案。<br />\n其實失業人士自殺，勞工福利局局長一定要問責。<br />\n至於失戀人士自殺，則與香港的教育制度欠缺男女關係教育引起，亦跟部分流行曲鼓吹為愛人「死也願意」，「生存只因可為你生」可能有關。<br />\n這些歌曲終日在傳媒(包括香港電台）反覆播放，政府視而不見，有關官員實是罪無可恕。<br />\n在此，亦希望特區政府立即交代其防止自殺政策。"},{"pid":"b6d85e4eda60d2ed2a2cc8d1197d1777c4ac3fb0","tid":96972,"uid":23785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:27:42.000Z","msg":"生涯規劃"},{"pid":"6c4c8f2cbfb7b3be4c4459dee02264f5f00565eb","tid":96972,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:28:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生涯規劃</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點規劃？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2657438454649ce76b4c4b4baf4a4eb98a8969b","tid":96972,"uid":23785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:35:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>生涯規劃</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點規劃？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你問吳克儉"},{"pid":"f324448a363c0b51f451eebd8d6696b26b58f022","tid":96972,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T10:41:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dde5e6a32004be1ced2dc91f9e8f5d26dc7254bb","tid":96972,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-